summary: Simple mod that creates a new NPC
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds to skyrim a chef named Jammy. He can be found in the Whiterun Stables.
Jammy is pretty pointless, but he is hilarious. He has the voice of a prepubescent, and is very fun to kill. This was my first mod, so it is pretty simple, but I am working on a bigger one now. Thanks :D.
INSTALLATION:
Step 1: Un-Zip file and place Jammy.esp on desktop
Step 2: Open you skyrim data folder, usually at
C:Program Files (x86)SteamSteamAppscommonSkyrimData
Step 3: Place Jammy.esp in that folder
Step 4: When you launch SKyrim, select JAMMY from where
you normally select mods
ENJOY :D
author: willfavre4
